"data/events_special_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"GUARD_AEA_SHARD_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr "你击败了碎晶锻者守卫。无论他们货舱中曾有何物，已损毁殆尽，但你至少能从星舰上"
"回收部分物资。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_shard.xml:152
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"GUARD_AEA_SHARD_DESTROY\"]/choice/text"
